{"tid":1459152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好唔記得港航財政好脆弱","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:41:56.000Z","uid":259120,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"93e5dd1aa31e5650b003d654617a35b42766ebf8","tid":1459152,"uid":259120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"當大家都focus 左去國泰內部電郵果陣<br />\n唔好唔記得港航五月時連油錢都畀唔到<br />\n如果港航因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持續</span></strong>既機場集會搞到資金鏈斷裂，執笠係唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n除左要回機票，有機場巴絲已經講EU 要每人賠600 歐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢件事最 fascinating 既地方係港航一出事，因為背後既海航集團本身已經用盡子公司去做抵押，會造成骨牌效應，什麼推冧整個海航一啲都唔奇<br />\n<br />\n其實海航7月已經有15億人仔債務違約<br />\n可以search 16海航02<br />\n唔知今日還左未，如果未，有人話到8月18都未找到，海航可以話玩完<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/28248/%E6%94%AF%E7%88%86-%E8%88%87%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F28248%2F%25E6%2594%25AF%25E7%2588%2586-%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%2588%25AA&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=83fb672e\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/28248/%E6%94%AF%E7%88%86-%E8%88%87%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我覺得林鄭佢地係驚海航爆煲，多過機場聲譽又或者經濟。始終送中都出得。"},{"pid":"a86ce5b7b4e6d7d174cd59f90106a134c0bdc380","tid":1459152,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fa3ea6e19c403d003533ce49ae909958ca365b9","tid":1459152,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"961f40d326963c2f1d859ca833dc380737487c1f","tid":1459152,"uid":25